'''奥姆兰·达克尼什'''（{{lang-ar|عمران دقنيش}}，{{lang-en|Omran Daqneesh}}）是一名[[叙利亚人|叙利亚]]男孩，[[2016年|2016年]]时年5岁的他遭到[[空袭|空袭]]，受伤后的他坐在一张橙色救护车椅子上，身上布满灰尘和血，没有哭喊。<ref name="sohu">{{cite web|author1=祖晓雯|title=阿勒颇男孩拍摄者：照片是真的，希望停止轰炸-搜狐新闻|url=http://news.sohu.com/20160824/n465682383.shtml|website=news.sohu.com|publisher=地球外参|accessdate=2017-04-07|location=北京|language=Zh-hans|date=2016-08-24|archive-date=2019-03-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190331092838/http://news.sohu.com/20160824/n465682383.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>他的视频被传到互联网上后受到媒体关注。<ref>{{cite news|title=Boy in the ambulance: shocking image emerges of Syrian child pulled from Aleppo rubble|url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2016/aug/18/boy-in-the-ambulance-image-emerges-syrian-child-aleppo-rubble|work=卫报|accessdate=2016-08-18|archive-date=2016-08-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160818061048/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2016/aug/18/boy-in-the-ambulance-image-emerges-syrian-child-aleppo-rubble|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2016/08/19/world/middleeast/omran-daqneesh-syria-aleppo.html|title=How Omran Daqneesh, 5, Became a Symbol of Aleppo's Suffering|date=2016-08-19|work=纽约时报|accessdate=2016-08-20|archive-date=2016-08-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160820015832/http://www.nytimes.com/2016/08/19/world/middleeast/omran-daqneesh-syria-aleppo.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 历史 ==
2016年8月17日，[[俄罗斯空军|俄罗斯空军]]空袭[[叙利亚|叙利亚]][[阿勒颇|阿勒颇]]附近由叛军控制的卡特吉<ref>{{cite news|title=Врач в Алеппо: пятилетнему малышу на видео крупно повезло|url=http://www.bbc.com/russian/features-37132058|accessdate=2017-04-07|work=BBC Русская служба|publisher=BBC俄罗斯|language=ru|date=2016-08-19|archive-date=2018-03-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180322065232/http://www.bbc.com/russian/features-37132058|dead-url=no}}</ref>，达克尼什受伤。他头部受伤，被送往一家被称为M10的医院，后来出院。

达克尼什与他父母和三个年龄为一岁、六岁和十岁的兄弟被救出。他十岁的哥哥阿里受伤并于2016年8月20日死亡。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Katie|first1=Reilly|title=Brother of Aleppo Boy in Ambulance Dies|url=http://time.com/4460368/ali-daqneesh-dead-syrian-air-strike/|work=时代周刊|date=2016-08-21|accessdate=2017-04-07|archive-date=2020-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201201214544/https://time.com/4460368/ali-daqneesh-dead-syrian-air-strike/|dead-url=no}}</ref>他家被救出后不久，公寓大楼倒塌。空袭造成八人死亡，其中五名儿童。达克尼什的视频由[[叙利亚反对派|叙利亚反对派]]活动小组阿勒颇媒体中心发布，作者是马哈茂德·拉斯兰（{{lang|en|Mahmoud Raslan}}）。<ref name="sohu" />

从他家的瓦砾中被救出的达克尼什坐在救护车血淋淋的照片，<ref>{{cite news|last1=Shaheen|first1=Kareem|title='I filmed the Syrian boy pulled from the rubble - his wasn't a rare case'|url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2016/aug/18/i-filmed-the-syrian-boy-pulled-from-the-rubble-his-wasnt-a-rare-case|work=卫报|date=2016-08-18|accessdate=2017-04-07|archive-date=2016-08-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160823015706/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2016/aug/18/i-filmed-the-syrian-boy-pulled-from-the-rubble-his-wasnt-a-rare-case|dead-url=no}}</ref>引起了国际公愤，并被广泛刊登在报纸和社交媒体上。很多人将他与逃往欧洲途中溺死的[[敘利亞內戰難民|敘利亞內戰難民]]小男孩[[艾兰·库尔迪之死|艾兰·库尔迪]]的照片作比较。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Barnard|first1=Anne|title=How Omran Daqneesh, 5, Became a Symbol of Aleppo’s Suffering|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2016/08/19/world/middleeast/omran-daqneesh-syria-aleppo.html|accessdate=2017-04-07|work=纽约时报|date=2016-08-18|archive-date=2016-08-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160820015832/http://www.nytimes.com/2016/08/19/world/middleeast/omran-daqneesh-syria-aleppo.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

叙利亚政府的盟友中国和俄罗斯媒体称图片为反对派的“宣传”工具，旨在利用这张照片，反对阿萨德政府的政权。<ref name="sohu" />一些国际媒体质疑图片为摆拍。<ref name="sohu" /><ref>{{cite news|title=China says Omran images are part of Western 'propaganda war'|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/middle-east/omran-daqneesh-photo-video-aleppo-boy-syria-injured-china-state-media-western-propaganda-war-a7205296.html|accessdate=2017-04-07|work=独立报|date=2016-08-23|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108092933/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/middle-east/omran-daqneesh-photo-video-aleppo-boy-syria-injured-china-state-media-western-propaganda-war-a7205296.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

敘政府軍[[阿勒頗攻勢_(2016年9月－12月)|收復阿勒頗]]後，達克尼什一家留在阿勒頗生活。2017年間，達克尼什的父親接受多間媒體採訪，反駁2016年西方媒體對事發經過的描述。達克尼什指事發時沒有空襲或炮擊，並指敘反對派曾試圖威逼利誘他，要求他對媒體指證敘政府軍發動襲擊，但遭到他拒絕。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/world/2017-08/17/c_129683491.htm |title=让世界揪心的叙利亚男孩 不做谎言“代言人” |publisher=新華網 |date=2017-08-17 |accessdate=2017-08-22 |archive-date=2017-08-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170822180404/http://news.xinhuanet.com/world/2017-08/17/c_129683491.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>

